# Optional: a dedicated Solana RPC endpoint used by the in-page Jupiter swap.
# The public endpoint is heavily rate-limited and often blocks swaps, so a
# dedicated RPC (Helius, QuickNode, Triton, Alchemy, …) is strongly recommended.
# Copy this file to `.env` and set your URL:
VITE_SOLANA_RPC=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
